<abstract>
Saint Matthew's Episcopal Church, located in Sparta, MI, was established 1955 and disbanded in 2003. The record group contains annual reports, bulletins, clergy reports, correspondence, financial records, meeting minutes, newsletters, and various administrative documents.</abstract>


